{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-contents-markdown-remark-frontmatter-slug-tsx","path":"/contents/16th-algorithm-study-memoir/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"좋은-문제집을-소개받다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A2%8B%EC%9D%80-%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C%EC%A7%91%EC%9D%84-%EC%86%8C%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9B%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"좋은 문제집을 소개받다 permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>좋은 문제집을 소개받다.</h1>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 420px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/37609d4f3796c53861cc60db776a68eb/29229/2022-ch-1.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 45.714285714285715%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='충남대학교 SW-IT 문제집' title='충남대학교 SW-IT 문제집' src='/static/37609d4f3796c53861cc60db776a68eb/d10fb/2022-ch-1.png' srcset='/static/37609d4f3796c53861cc60db776a68eb/79c17/2022-ch-1.png 105w,\n/static/37609d4f3796c53861cc60db776a68eb/65ed1/2022-ch-1.png 210w,\n/static/37609d4f3796c53861cc60db776a68eb/d10fb/2022-ch-1.png 420w,\n/static/37609d4f3796c53861cc60db776a68eb/f058b/2022-ch-1.png 630w,\n/static/37609d4f3796c53861cc60db776a68eb/1e088/2022-ch-1.png 840w,\n/static/37609d4f3796c53861cc60db776a68eb/29229/2022-ch-1.png 1167w' sizes='(max-width: 420px) 100vw, 420px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\r\n스터디 원 중에 해당 정보를 확인하고 공유해준 충대 22년 SW-IT-Contest 토대로 일단 간단하게 3문제\r\n진행해봤다.</p>\n<p>많이 들어왔던 엘리트 충대라 첫 문제부터 각오하고 들어갔는데 생각보다 난이도는 괜찮았다.</p>\n<p>사진 자료 상 2문제는 너무 쉬웠으므로 간단한 스택문제인 \"균형 잡힌 소떡소떡\" 만 짚어가겠다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"25641-균형-잡힌-소떡소떡-boj\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#25641-%EA%B7%A0%ED%98%95-%EC%9E%A1%ED%9E%8C-%EC%86%8C%EB%96%A1%EC%86%8C%EB%96%A1-boj\" aria-label=\"25641 균형 잡힌 소떡소떡 boj permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>25641. 균형 잡힌 소떡소떡 [BOJ]</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.acmicpc.net/problem/25641\">균형 잡힌 소떡소떡</a>\r\n<span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 420px; '>\n      <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 68.57142857142857%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='소떡문제 이미지' title='소떡문제 이미지' src='/static/bb1e15148aa7f770b25106ebd5791227/d10fb/stst_detail.png' srcset='/static/bb1e15148aa7f770b25106ebd5791227/79c17/stst_detail.png 105w,\n/static/bb1e15148aa7f770b25106ebd5791227/65ed1/stst_detail.png 210w,\n/static/bb1e15148aa7f770b25106ebd5791227/d10fb/stst_detail.png 420w,\n/static/bb1e15148aa7f770b25106ebd5791227/f058b/stst_detail.png 630w,\n/static/bb1e15148aa7f770b25106ebd5791227/1e088/stst_detail.png 840w,\n/static/bb1e15148aa7f770b25106ebd5791227/8a69d/stst_detail.png 1209w' sizes='(max-width: 420px) 100vw, 420px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n    </span></p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"c\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"material\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">using namespace std;\r\n\r\nint main() {\r\n  ios::sync_with_stdio(false);\r\n  cin.tie(nullptr);\r\n  stack&lt;char&gt; S;\r\n  int t_count = 0, s_count = 0;\r\n  string T;\r\n  cin &gt;&gt; T;\r\n  string ST;\r\n  cin &gt;&gt; ST;\r\n\r\n  for (int i = ST.length() - 1; i &gt;= 0; i--) {\r\n    char c = ST[i];\r\n    if (c == &#39;t&#39;) t_count++;\r\n    else s_count++;\r\n    S.push(ST[i]);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  while (t_count != s_count) {\r\n    if (S.top() == &#39;t&#39;) t_count--;\r\n    else s_count--;\r\n    S.pop();\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  while (!S.empty()) {\r\n    cout &lt;&lt; S.top();\r\n    S.pop();\r\n  }\r\n  cout &lt;&lt; endl;\r\n}\r\n</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>정말 반가운 스택문제다.</p>\n<p>나는 스택문제가 좋다 ㅎㅎ</p>\n<p>처음에 좌측 재료를 뺄 때 소시지(S)를 빼야하는데 떡(T) 이 있으면 떡을 빼놓고,</p>\n<p>소시지(S) 빠지면 뺀 떡(T)을 다시 밀어넣어야하는 줄 알고 괴상한 로직을 작성했다 ㅎㅎ;</p>\n<p>자신감 채우는 하루였다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"날로먹었어\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%82%A0%EB%A1%9C%EB%A8%B9%EC%97%88%EC%96%B4\" aria-label=\"날로먹었어 permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>날로먹었어?</h1>\n<p>스터디 조건은 만족했지만 이걸 알고리즘 공부했다고 하긴 민망하다.</p>\n<p>사실 우리 스터디는 여유롭게 가면서 노 커리큘럼 체계긴 하다.</p>\n<p>게으르게 한 주를 보낸 건 아니다.</p>\n<p>급작스럽게 스프링 개발을 총괄담당하게 되었고, 홈쇼핑 프로젝트 프런트엔드 작업하느라 바빴다.</p>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 420px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/2a730094d6773ff57e1f72b130eef676/a016c/my_condition.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='내 풀이 현황 이미지' title='내 풀이 현황 이미지' src='/static/2a730094d6773ff57e1f72b130eef676/d10fb/my_condition.png' srcset='/static/2a730094d6773ff57e1f72b130eef676/79c17/my_condition.png 105w,\n/static/2a730094d6773ff57e1f72b130eef676/65ed1/my_condition.png 210w,\n/static/2a730094d6773ff57e1f72b130eef676/d10fb/my_condition.png 420w,\n/static/2a730094d6773ff57e1f72b130eef676/f058b/my_condition.png 630w,\n/static/2a730094d6773ff57e1f72b130eef676/a016c/my_condition.png 762w' sizes='(max-width: 420px) 100vw, 420px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"참고 permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://alg-study-helper-chi.vercel.app/\">알고리즘 스터디 웹 서비스</a></p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%A2%8B%EC%9D%80-%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C%EC%A7%91%EC%9D%84-%EC%86%8C%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9B%EB%8B%A4\">좋은 문제집을 소개받다.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#25641-%EA%B7%A0%ED%98%95-%EC%9E%A1%ED%9E%8C-%EC%86%8C%EB%96%A1%EC%86%8C%EB%96%A1-boj\">25641. 균형 잡힌 소떡소떡 [BOJ]</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EB%82%A0%EB%A1%9C%EB%A8%B9%EC%97%88%EC%96%B4\">날로먹었어?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\">참고</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"11월 1주차 알고리즘 스터디 회고록","date":"2022년 11월 04일","slug":"16th-algorithm-study-memoir","tag":["Algorithm"]}}},"pageContext":{"id":"2366cae4-eb91-5a29-91e2-fa46331f2e7f","frontmatter__slug":"16th-algorithm-study-memoir","__params":{"frontmatter__slug":"16th-algorithm-study-memoir"}}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}